#. Tag: title
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "With NFS"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Refer to the documentation provided with the third party product that "
"enables NFS server services for your Windows workstation. The DVD-ROM drive "
"containing the &productname; DVDs must be in the available NFS path."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "With FTP"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Refer to the documentation provided with the third party product that is "
"enabling FTP server services on your Windows workstation. The DVD-ROM drive "
"containing the &productname; DVDs must be in the available FTP path."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The FTP server that is bundled with some Microsoft Windows releases "
"implements only a subset of the FTP command set and is not suitable for "
"providing the installation data. If this applies to your Windows "
"workstation, use a third party FTP server providing the required features."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using an FCP-Attached SCSI DVD Drive"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you IPLed from the SCSI DVD as described in <xref linkend=\"sec.info."
"iplopt.dvd\"/>, the installation system uses the DVD as the installation "
"medium. In that case, you do not need the installation media on an FTP, NFS, "
"or SMB server. However, you need the network configuration data for your "
"&productname;, because you must set up the network during the installation "
"to perform a graphical installation by VNC or by X."
msgstr ""

