#. Tag: para
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:1056
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When all network device parameters have been entered, the respective driver "
"is installed and you see the corresponding kernel messages."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:1060
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, decide whether to use DHCP autoconfiguration for setting up the "
"network interface parameters. Because DHCP only works on a few devices and "
"requires special hardware configuration settings, you probably want to say "
"<guimenu>NO</guimenu> here. When you do so, you are prompted for the "
"following networking parameters:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:1069
#, no-c-format
msgid "The IP address of the system to install"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:1074
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The corresponding netmask (if not having been specified with the IP address)"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:1080
#, no-c-format
msgid "The IP address of a gateway to reach the server"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_prep_zseries_prep_i.xml:1085
#, no-c-format
msgid "A list of search domains covered by the domain name server (DNS)"
